=== SugarCRM/SuiteCRM Customer Portal ===
Contributors: biztechc
Tags: SugarCRM/SuiteCRM Customer Portal,sugarcrm,suitecrm,CRM,Case
Requires at least: 3.6.1
Tested up to: 4.7
Stable tag: 2.1.1
License: GPLv2 or later
 
This plug-in use for sugarcrm. It manage Cases services-releated problems reported by your users and customers.  
 
== Description ==
 
The integration of WordPress and Sugar/SuiteCRM can help Sugar/SuiteCRM users to manage their WordPress customer's complaints by offering them a WordPress interactive interface where they can lodge their complaints and keep track of the current status and latest development.
 
This plugin will automatically creates all required pages with shortcodes.You can use these shortcodes in your custom template too.
 
Below is a list of all shortcodes used in plugin.

1. sign up [bcp-sign-up]
2. Login [bcp-login]
3. Forgot Password : [bcp-forgot-password]
4. Dashboard : [bcp-dashboard-gui]
5. Manage Page : [bcp-manage-page]
6. Profile : [bcp-profile]
 
= Handling Customer Grievances Made Easier =
 
If you’re a Sugar/SuiteCRM user and have a huge repository of customers to handle, directly interacting with them could often be difficult as they cannot access your Sugar/SuiteCRM database.
 
But with WP Sugar/SuiteCRM integration you can now handle your customers’ cases easily and quickly. This Sugar/SuiteCRM Customer Portal can help you provide your customers an interactive WP interface, which will be synced with your Sugar/SuiteCRM portal. Using this interface they can lodge their complaints, which can be viewed and sorted out by you as this plugin will be synced with your Sugar/SuiteCRM portal.
 
This will help your customers to create their case and profile, which they can also update and keep track of. They will also be able to view the current status and comments, if any, that you make using your Sugar/SuiteCRM portal.
 
= Core Features =
1. View all cases assigned to the user
2. User can create cases.
3. Users can create their profile and update it
4. Can post their cases and track the latest updates
5. Template selection for better GUI
 
= Users’ Gain =
1. It helps Sugar/SuiteCRM users to communicate with their customers easily in case of any complaints
2. End users can lodge their complaints easily and convey the message to their vendors
3. This helps both the customers and their end users to retain their relations by resolving the complaints and maintaining customer loyalty.
 
